ZH: 我的工作负担很重，每天都非常忙碌。
EN: My work burden is heavy, and I am busy every day.

ZH: 这个家庭的开销对我来说是一个巨大的负担。
EN: The expenses of this household are a huge burden for me.

ZH: 学生应该能够承担自己的学习负担。
EN: Students should be able to handle their own academic burden.

ZH: 贷款利息是买房的一个额外负担。
EN: Loan interest is an additional burden when buying a house.

ZH: 他一直承担着全家的经济负担。
EN: He has been shouldering the financial burden of the whole family.

ZH: 这个项目的执行很有挑战性，给我们增加了许多负担。
EN: The execution of this project is very challenging and adds a lot of burden to us.

ZH: 妈妈总是为家里的家务负担而烦恼。
EN: Mom is always worried about the burden of household chores.

ZH: 购物中心日常的维护费用是商家们的负担。
EN: The maintenance cost of the shopping center is a burden for the merchants.

ZH: 有时候，照顾老人是孩子们的负担。
EN: Sometimes, taking care of the elderly becomes a burden for the children.

ZH: 他很慷慨地承担了朋友们的婚宴费用，分担了他们的负担。
EN: He generously took on the burden of his friends' wedding banquet expenses, lightening their burden.

ZH: 工作压力太大，我感到了沉重的负担。
EN: The work pressure is too high, and I feel a heavy burden.

ZH: 这次考试给学生们增加了很大的负担。
EN: This exam has added a great burden to the students.

ZH: 负担太重，让我感到无法承受。
EN: The burden is too heavy, making me feel overwhelmed.

ZH: 因为负担太重，他决定辞掉工作。
EN: Because the burden was too heavy, he decided to quit his job.

ZH: 她给了我很多的帮助，减轻了我的负担。
EN: She gave me a lot of help, lightening my burden.

ZH: 这项计划将把负担转移到其他部门。
EN: This plan will shift the burden to other departments.

ZH: 他经常参加志愿者活动，为社区分担负担。
EN: He often participates in volunteer activities, sharing the burden for the community.

ZH: 每个人都要为环境保护负起责任和负担。
EN: Everyone has the responsibility and burden of protecting the environment.

ZH: 政府为贫困家庭提供了一定的生活负担救助。
EN: The government provides certain financial assistance to low-income families to alleviate their living burden.

ZH: 这次团队项目需要大家共同分担负担。
EN: This team project requires everyone to share the burden together.
